# CODEOWNERS file
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners (teams or users)
# These owners will be automatically requested for review when someone opens a PR that modifies files matching the pattern

# Backend team owns all backend code
/backend/ @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/backend-team

# Frontend team owns all frontend code
/frontend/ @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/frontend-team

# Mobile team owns all mobile code
/mobile/ @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/mobile-team

# ML team owns all machine learning code
/ml/ @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/ml-team

# Data team owns all data-related code
/data/ @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/data-team

# QA team owns all QA code and tests
/qa/ @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/qa-team

# SRE team owns all SRE infrastructure and helm charts
/sre/ @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/sre-team

# GitHub workflows and CI/CD - owned by SRE team
/.github/ @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/sre-team

# Root level files - require approval from multiple teams
/README.md @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/backend-team @tekmetric-org/frontend-team @tekmetric-org/sre-team
/.gitignore @actekmetric @tekmetric-org/sre-team

